Package: glcm
Version: 1.3
Date: 2015-11-20
Title: Calculate Textures from Grey-Level Co-occurrence Matrices (GLCMs)
Authors@R: person("Alex", "Zvoleff", email="azvoleff@conservation.org",
    role=c("aut", "cre"))
